yelb.yaml - NodePort Example

Step 1 - Create yelb NS
kubectl create ns yelb

Step 2 - Deploy Yelb App
kubectl apply -f yelb.yaml

Step 3 - Delete Yelb App
kubectl delete -f yelb.yaml


yelb-lb.yaml - Load Balancer Example

Step 0 - Ensure you've got Load Balancer service enabled. If you do not have one, take a look at metallb

Step 1 - Create yelb NS
kubectl create ns yelb

Step 2 - Deploy Yelb App
kubectl apply -f yelb-lb.yaml

Step 3 - Delete Yelb App
kubectl delete -f yelb-b.yaml